{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"d95d0d04-3026-411e-a640-4845faf1ec4b","content":"Yes, you'll hit compatibility issues. Here's the breakdown:\n\n**Framework Support Dropped in MSTest v3:**\n\n| Target | Status |\n|---|---|\n| `net462` | ✅ Supported |\n| `net5.0` | ❌ Dropped (.NET 5 is EOL) |\n| `netcoreapp3.1` | ❌ Dropped (.NET Core 3.1 is EOL) |\n\nMSTest v3 requires **.NET Framework 4.6.2+** or **.NET 6.0+**. Two of your three targets (`net5.0` and `netcoreapp3.1`) are unsupported.\n\n**To migrate, you'd need to:**\n1. Replace `net5.0` → `net6.0` (or later) and `netcoreapp3.1` → `net6.0` (or later).\n2. Replace the two package references with the single `MSTest` meta-package (v3+).\n\n**Other MSTest v3 breaking changes to watch for:**\n- `ClassCleanupBehavior` default changed to `EndOfClass`.\n- Some assert APIs have updated signatures.\n- `DataRow` attribute no longer supports `DynamicData`-style complex objects.\n\nWould you like me to update the `.csproj` to MSTest v3?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"2cdba2c9-17ff-484f-aa58-854386c0111f","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user's project targets:\n- net5.0\n- net462\n- netcoreapp3.1\n\nAnd uses MSTest v2 (2.2.10). Let me think about what compatibility issues they'll face with MSTest v3.\n\nMSTest v3 dropped support for older target frameworks. Specifically:\n- .NET 5.0 is not supported (it's out of support)\n- .NET Core 3.1 is not supported (it's out of support)\n- .NET Framework 4.6.2 — MSTest v3 requires .NET Framework 4.6.2+ so this should still be supported. Actually, let me double-check. \n\nMSTest v3 supports .NET Framework 4.6.2 and later, so net462 is fine, but the real problem is that netcoreapp3.1 and net5.0 are both end-of-life frameworks that MSTest v3 no longer supports—only .NET 6.0 and newer are compatible.\n\nAlso, MSTest v3 consolidated its package structure into a single `MSTest` meta-package, though the older separate packages still work if needed.","outputTokens":717,"requestId":"042B:22EFE:5FC8E2:709532:69E83213"},"id":"850dfbcc-02b0-49c1-9990-3bd0e1025e2c","timestamp":"2026-04-22T02:27:46.196Z","parentId":"7873792b-9086-4da8-8c7e-d764944263f2"}
